symbol.name: Symbol
symbol.desc: Buys a custom symbol to go infront of your username and puts you at top of userlist.

avatar.name: Avatar
avatar.desc: Buys an custom avatar to be applied to your name.

animatedavatar.name: Animated Avatar
animatedavatar.desc: Buys an custom animted avatar to be applied to your name.

customtitle.name: Custom Title
customtitle.desc: Buys a title to be added on to your profile

customcolor.name: Custom Color
customcolor.desc: Changes the color of your name.

icon.name: Icon
icon.desc: Buy a custom icon that can be applied to the rooms you want. You must take into account that the provided image should be 32 x 32.

room.name: Room
room.desc: Buys a chatroom for you to own.

profileteam.name: Profile Team
profileteam.desc: Buys you ability to set your profile team.

roomshop.name: Room Shop
roomshop.desc: Buys a Roomshop for your League or Room.

emote.name: Emote
emote.desc: You provide an image (50x50 Pixels) to be added as an emote on the server.

chatcolor.name: Chat Color
chatcolor.desc: Allows you to use chat colors.
